 2011-12-14 unsafe because not all functions use same namespace.
 .
 2011-12-14 The Upstream repository contains many many files that have
 othing to do with the package. Fortunately those directories are marked
 with .nosearch files and are interfore excluded by epackage-devel-*
 functions. It is better to not to clean up upstream code for the 'master'
 epackage branch. Upgrading upstream code stays this way easier to merge.
Description: major mode and client for Twitter
 Client interface to <http://twitter.ccom>. You can check friends timeline,
 and update your status.
 .
 Note: depends on external programs; curl, wget, gnutls, openssl (for encrypted
 connections).
